o\u00f1a]], [[Cantabria]]\n*[[Figueres Prison]], [[Figueres]], [[Province of Girona|Girona]]\n*[[Girona Prison]], [[Girona]]\n*[[Estremera Prison]], [[Estremera]], [[Community of Madrid]]\n*[[Herrera de la Mancha Prison]], [[Manzanares, Ciudad Real|Manzanares]], [[Province of Ciudad Real|Ciudad Real]]\n*[[Huelva Prison]], [[Huelva]]\n*[[Ibiza Prison]], [[Ibiza]], [[Balearic Islands]]\n*[[Ja\u00e9n Prison]], [[Ja\u00e9n, Spain|Ja\u00e9n]]\n*[[La Moraleja Prison]], [[Due\u00f1as, Palencia|Due\u00f1as]], [[Province of Palencia|Palencia]]\n*[[Lledoners Prison]], [[Sant Joan de Vilatorrada]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n*[[Lleida Prison]], [[Lleida]]\n*[[Las Palmas Prison]], [[Las Palmas de Gran Canaria]]\n*[[Logro\u00f1o Prison]], [[Logro\u00f1o]], [[La Rioja (Spain)|La Rioja]]\n*[[Mansilla de las Mulas Prison]], [[Mansilla de las Mulas]], [[Province of Le\u00f3n|L\u00e9on]]\n*[[Melilla Prison]], [[Melilla]]\n*[[Monterroso Prison]], [[Monterroso]], [[Province of Lugo|Lugo]]\n*[[Mor\u00f3n de la Frontera Prison]], [[Mor\u00f3n de la Frontera]], [[Province of Seville|Seville]]\n*[[Murcia Prison]], [[Murcia]]\n*[[Nanclares de la Oca Prison]], [[Langraiz-Oka]], [[\u00c1lava]]\n*[[Navalcarnero Prison]], [[Navalcarnero]], [[Community of Madrid]]\n*[[Oca\u00f1a Prison]], [[Oca\u00f1a, Spain|Oca\u00f1a]], [[Province of Toledo|Toledo]]\n*[[Palma Prison]], [[Palma, Majorca|Palma]], [[Balearic Islands]]\n*[[Pamplona Prison]], [[Pamplona]], [[Navarre]]\n*[[Pereiro de Aguiar Prison]], [[Pereiro de Aguiar]], [[Province of Ourense|Ourense]]\n*[[Puerto Prison]], [[Puerto de Santa Mar\u00eda]], [[Province of C\u00e1diz|C\u00e1diz]]\n*[[Quatre Camins Prison]], [[la Roca del Vall\u00e8s]], [[Province of Barcelona|Barcelona]]\n*[[San Sebasti\u00e1n Prison]], [[San Sebasti\u00e1n]], [[Gipuzkoa]]\n*[[Santa Cruz de la Palma Prison]], [[Santa Cruz de la Palma]], [[Province of Santa Cruz de Tenerife|Santa Cruz de Tenerife]]\n*[[Santa Cruz de Tenerife Prison]], [[El Rosario, Tenerife|El